author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Gallowstreet performing live at the l’Antipode in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2024. Recorded December 6, 2024. 

Songs:
Assemble 00:09
Proper Hired Guns 05:40
Phoenix 09:59
Diesel 17:05

Colin Vermeulen - Drums
Jeroen Vermazeren - Sousaphone
Jeroen Verberne - Trombone

Dirk Zandvliet - Bar Sax, Flute
Dima Loginov - Trumpet
